ky Way's thick and thin discs\ncan be explained entirely as imprints by the star-forming ISM, rather than by\nmergers or secular processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 18:00:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
