endence on the number of points in the\ntemporal direction ($N_\\tau$) adopted in the lattice simulation and $N_\\tau$\nlarger than 48 is needed to resolve the fate of $\\eta_c$ at 1.5 $T_c$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Oct 2021 09:23:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 11 Jun 2022 08:29:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 13:44:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-23"}
